t: The History of Samson | Samson Exhaust
s: An American brand is born. In 1991 Samson Motorcycle Products was founded by Kenny Price, later to be known as “The Godfather of Pipes”. Kenny’s mission was to build great looking pipes that would not break. At the time, exhaust pipes breaking while on the road was a common occurrence.
